"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"id\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Ruang Kapernaum</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f4f4;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: white;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        .room-name {\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #000000;\n        }\n\n        .room-description {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: #000000;\n    \n        }\n\n        .room-description p {\n          text-align: justify;\n          text-justify: auto;\n          text-indent: 10%;\n        }\n\n        .image-section {\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .image-container {\n            flex-basis: 100%;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .image-container img {\n            width: 90%;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .image-caption {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #000000;\n        }\n\n        @media only screen and (min-width: 600px) {\n            /* Jika layar lebih besar dari 600px (misalnya tablet atau layar lebih besar) */\n            .container {\n                max-width: 600px;\n            }\n\n            .image-section {\n              width: 100%;\n              border-radius: 10px;\n              margin-bottom: 20px;\n            }\n\n            .image-container {\n                flex-basis: 48%;\n                margin-bottom: 0;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n\n</head>\n\n<body>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"room-name\">Ruang Kapernaum</div>\n        <div class=\"room-description\">\n          <p>Tempat Tuhan Yesus berkiprah, setelah Yohanes Pembaptis ditangkap. Di sana Tuhan Yesus banyak melakukan karya dan mukjizat. Diharapkan tambahan ruangan baru ini menjadi berkat untuk pelayanan GKI Salatiga. Sebelumnya dikenal dengan nama <b>Ruang Serbaguna</b> (ruangan yang terbaru).</p></br>\n          <b>Pemakaian</b> : Rapat, pelatihan, pembinaan, dan donor darah.\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"image-section\">\n            <div class=\"image-container\">\n                <img src=\"https://github.com/gkisalatiga/gkisplus-data/blob/main/images-profile/ruang_kapernaum_1.jpg?raw=true\" alt=\"Tampak Depan\">\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">Tampak Depan</div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"image-container\">\n                <img src=\"https://github.com/gkisalatiga/gkisplus-data/blob/main/images-profile/ruang_kapernaum_2.jpg?raw=true\" alt=\"Tampak Dalam\">\n                <div class=\"image-caption\">Tampak Dalam</div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>"